---
import Layout from "../components/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Epistola · Terms" description="Usage terms for the Epistola website, demo environment, and commercial support offerings.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Terms</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">
        Terms of use
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-10 text-[var(--color-gray-700)] dark:text-white/80">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">Open-source usage</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Epistola’s source code is licensed under the AGPL. You are free to self-host, modify, and redistribute the software under that license. Contributions are accepted via GitHub.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">Demo environment</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The public demo is provided “as is.” We may reset, limit, or suspend access if the environment is misused. Do not store sensitive information in the demo instance.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">Commercial support</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Support and managed hosting plans are governed by separate service agreements. Those agreements outline SLAs, pricing, and acceptable use.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">Liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Epistola and its contributors are not liable for any damages arising from the use of the open-source software, the demo environment, or third-party integrations.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-gray-900)] dark:text-white">Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            For contractual questions, reach out to <a class="underline hover:text-[var(--color-brand-600)]" href="mailto:hello@epistola.app">hello@epistola.app</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
